---
title: Sticky Hoisin Glazed Chicken  with Sriracha Mayo, Zesty Rice and Sesame Seeds
description: Hoisin contains Chinese Five Spice, rice vinegar and red miso which gives it its delicious sweet-umami flavour. Here, we're reducing it down whilst the chicken is in the pan to coat it in an easy sticky glaze.
